hardinfo2 (System Information and Benchmark for Linux Systems)

Hardinfo2 offers System Information and Benchmark for Linux Systems.
It is able to obtain information from both hardware and basic
software. It can benchmark your system and compare to other machines
online.
Features include:
- Report generation (in either HTML or plain text)
- Online Benchmarking - compare your machine against other machines

HOME: https://hardinfo2.org/

======================================================================
REQUIRES: libdecor sysbench 

